# 🏢 Apogei 94 - Établissements & Dispositifs Page
*With Real Filtering Functionality | Aligned with tokens.json & theme.json*

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Nos Établissements & Dispositifs - Apogei 94</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Trouvez l'établissement ou le dispositif d'accompagnement adapté dans le Val-de-Marne">
    <style>
        /* -------------------------------------------------------------------------- */
        /* DESIGN SYSTEM TOKENS (From tokens.json & theme.json)                       */
        /* -------------------------------------------------------------------------- */
        :root {
            /* Colors - Mapped from theme.json palette */
            --color-bg-default: #f9f9f9;
            --color-bg-surface: #ffffff;
            --color-bg-subtle: #f3f3f3;
            --color-bg-muted: #e5e5e5;
