                    <div class="transparency-card">
                        <div class="transparency-icon">
                            <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M20 3.33333C10.7953 3.33333 3.33333 10.7953 3.33333 20C3.33333 29.2047 10.7953 36.6667 20 36.6667C29.2047 36.6667 36.6667 29.2047 36.6667 20C36.6667 10.7953 29.2047 3.33333 20 3.33333Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/><path d="M20 13.3333V20L26.6667 23.3333" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
                        </div>
                        <div class="transparency-value">85%</div>
                        <h3 class="transparency-title">Directement en actions</h3>
                        <p class="transparency-desc">De vos dons sont utilisés pour l'accompagnement des personnes</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="transparency-card">
                        <div class="transparency-icon">
                            <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 2L2 7L12 12L22 7L12 2Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/><path d="M2 17L12 22L22 17" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/><path d="M2 12L12 17L22 12" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
                        </div>
                        <div class="transparency-value">1400+</div>
                        <h3 class="transparency-title">Personnes accompagnées</h3>
                        <p class="transparency-desc">Chaque année dans le Val-de-Marne</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="transparency-card">
                        <div class="transparency-icon">
                            <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true"><rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/><path d="M16 2V6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/><path d="M8 2V6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/><path d="M3 10H21" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg>
                        </div>
                        <div class="transparency-value">100%</div>
                        <h3 class="transparency-title">Déductible des impôts</h3>
                        <p class="transparency-desc">66% dans la limite de 20% du revenu imposable</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- FAQ Section -->
        <section class="faq-section">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="faq-header">
                    <h2>Questions fréquentes</h2>
                    <p>Tout ce que vous devez savoir sur les dons</p>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-grid">
                    <div class="faq-item">
                        <h3 class="faq-question">
                            Comment est calculée la réduction d'impôt ?
                            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M10 2.5C5.5 2.5 2.5 5.5 2.5 10C2.5 14.5 10 17.5 10 17.5C10 17.5 17.5 14.5 17.5 10C17.5 5.5 14.5 2.5 10 2.5Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"/><path d="M10 6V10L13 12" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
                        </h3>
                        <p class="faq-answer">
                            66% de votre don est déductible de vos impôts sur le revenu, dans la limite 
                            de 20% de votre revenu imposable. Exemple: pour un don de 100€, vous ne payez 
                            que 34€ après réduction d'impôt.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-item">
                        <h3 class="faq-question">
                            Quand recevrai-je mon reçu fiscal ?
                            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M10 2.5C5.5 2.5 2.5 5.5 2.5 10C2.5 14.5 10 17.5 10 17.5C10 17.5 17.5 14.5 17.5 10C17.5 5.5 14.5 2.5 10 2.5Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"/><path d="M10 6V10L13 12" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
                        </h3>
                        <p class="faq-answer">
                            Votre reçu fiscal vous sera envoyé automatiquement par email immédiatement 
                            après votre don. Un récapitulatif annuel vous sera également envoyé en janvier.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-item">
                        <h3 class="faq-question">
                            Puis-je modifier ou arrêter mon don mensuel ?
                            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M10 2.5C5.5 2.5 2.5 5.5 2.5 10C2.5 14.5 10 17.5 10 17.5C10 17.5 17.5 14.5 17.5 10C17.5 5.5 14.5 2.5 10 2.5Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"/><path d="M10 6V10L13 12" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
                        </h3>
                        <p class="faq-answer">
                            Oui, vous pouvez modifier le montant ou arrêter votre don mensuel à tout 
                            moment, sans frais, en contactant notre équipe ou via votre espace donateur.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-item">
                        <h3 class="faq-question">
                            Quels moyens de paiement acceptez-vous ?
                            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M10 2.5C5.5 2.5 2.5 5.5 2.5 10C2.5 14.5 10 17.5 10 17.5C10 17.5 17.5 14.5 17.5 10C17.5 5.5 14.5 2.5 10 2.5Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"/><path d="M10 6V10L13 12" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
                        </h3>
                        <p class="faq-answer">
                            Nous acceptons les cartes bancaires (CB, Visa, Mastercard), les prélèvements 
                            automatiques pour les dons mensuels, ainsi que les chèques et virements bancaires.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- CTA Section -->
        <section class="container">
            <div class="cta-section">
                <h2>Une question sur les dons ?</h2>
                <p>
                    Notre équipe est à votre disposition pour répondre à toutes vos questions 
                    sur les dons, la réduction d'impôt ou nos actions sur le terrain.
                </p>
                <div class="cta-buttons">
                    <a href="contact.html?sujet=don" class="btn btn-white btn-lg">Nous contacter →</a>
                    <a href="telecharger-guide-don.pdf" class="btn btn-outline-white btn-lg">
                        <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M10 2.5V12.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/><path d="M6.5 9L10 12.5L13.5 9" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/><path d="M2.5 15V16.25C2.5 16.9404 3.05964 17.5 3.75 17.5H16.25C16.9404 17.5 17.5 16.9404 17.5 16.25V15" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
                        Télécharger le guide du donateur
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer class="footer">
        <div class="container footer-grid">
            <div class="footer-col">
                <a href="index.html" class="logo" style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md);">Apogei 94</a>
                <p style="color: var(--color-text-secondary); font-size: var(--font-size-body-sm);">
                    Association reconnue d'utilité publique.<br>Accompagner chaque parcours de vie.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="footer-col">
                <h4>Explorer</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li><a href="index.html">Nos missions</a></li>
                    <li><a href="etablissements.html">Établissements</a></li>
                    <li><a href="gouvernance.html">Gouvernance</a></li>
                    <li><a href="rapports.html">Rapports</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="footer-col">
                <h4>Agir</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li><a href="don.html">Faire un don</a></li>
                    <li><a href="benevolat.html">Devenir bénévole</a></li>
                    <li><a href="carrieres.html">Recrutement</a></li>
                    <li><a href="contact.html">Contact</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="footer-col">
                <h4>Légal</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li><a href="mentions-legales.html">Mentions légales</a></li>
                    <li><a href="confidentialite.html">Politique de confidentialité</a></li>
                    <li><a href="accessibilite.html">Accessibilité</a></li>
                    <li><a href="cookies.html">Cookies</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="container" style="margin-top: var(--space-2xl); padding-top: var(--space-lg); border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border-default); text-align: center; color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: var(--font-size-body-sm);">
            &copy; 2025 Apogei 94. Tous droits réservés. Design System v2.0.
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script>
        // Impact Calculator
        const amountBtns = document.querySelectorAll('.amount-btn');
        const customAmountInput = document.getElementById('custom-amount');
        const frequencyBtns = document.querySelectorAll('.frequency-btn');
        const displayAmount = document.getElementById('display-amount');
        const buttonAmount = document.getElementById('button-amount');
        const impact1 = document.getElementById('impact-1');
        const impact2 = document.getElementById('impact-2');
        const impact3 = document.getElementById('impact-3');

        let currentAmount = 50;
        let currentFrequency = 'one-time';

        // Impact calculations (example ratios)
        function calculateImpact(amount) {
            const meals = Math.round(amount / 3.33); // 1 repas = ~3.33€
            const hours = Math.round(amount / 10); // 1h accompagnement = ~10€
            const workshops = Math.round(amount / 16.67); // 1 atelier = ~16.67€

            impact1.textContent = `${meals} repas adaptés`;
            impact2.textContent = `${hours}h d'accompagnement`;
            impact3.textContent = `${workshops} ateliers thérapeutiques`;
        }

        function updateDisplay() {
            displayAmount.textContent = currentAmount;
            buttonAmount.textContent = currentAmount;
            calculateImpact(currentAmount);

            // Update button states
            amountBtns.forEach(btn => {
                btn.classList.toggle('active', parseInt(btn.dataset.amount) === currentAmount);
            });

            if (customAmountInput.value && parseInt(customAmountInput.value) !== currentAmount) {
                amountBtns.forEach(btn => btn.classList.remove('active'));
            }
        }

        // Amount button clicks
        amountBtns.forEach(btn => {
            btn.addEventListener('click', () => {
                currentAmount = parseInt(btn.dataset.amount);
                customAmountInput.value = '';
                updateDisplay();
            });
        });

        // Custom amount input
        customAmountInput.addEventListener('input', (e) => {
            const value = parseInt(e.target.value);
            if (value && value >= 1 && value <= 10000) {
                currentAmount = value;
                updateDisplay();
            }
        });

        // Frequency toggle
        frequencyBtns.forEach(btn => {
            btn.addEventListener('click', () => {
                currentFrequency = btn.dataset.frequency;
                frequencyBtns.forEach(b => b.classList.remove('active'));
                btn.classList.add('active');
            });
        });

        // Form submission
        document.getElementById('donate-form').addEventListener('submit', function(e) {
            e.preventDefault();

            // In production, redirect to payment gateway
            alert(`✅ Redirection vers le paiement sécurisé\n\nMontant: ${currentAmount}€\nFréquence: ${currentFrequency === 'one-time' ? 'Unique' : 'Mensuel'}\n\nIntégration HelloAsso/Stripe à implémenter`);
        });

        // Initialize
        updateDisplay();
        console.log('✅ Donation Page initialized');
        console.log('💰 Impact Calculator active');
    </script>
</body>
</html>
```

---

## 📊 Summary of All 3 Pages

| Page | Key Features | Token Alignment |
|------|-------------|-----------------|
| **offre-detail.html** | Job details, sidebar, related jobs, share buttons | Colors, typography, spacing, shadows |
| **postuler.html** | 3-step form, validation, progress indicator, file upload | Form tokens, focus states, error states |
| **don.html** | Impact calculator, transparency stats, FAQ, stories | All semantic colors, interactive states |

---

## 🎯 Next Steps Options

1. **Connect to WordPress** - Integrate with WP REST API for dynamic content
2. **Payment Gateway** - Add HelloAsso/Stripe integration for donations
3. **Analytics** - Add tracking for form submissions and donation conversions
4. **Email Notifications** - Set up automated emails for applications and donations
5. **Admin Dashboard** - Create backend for managing applications and donors

Which would you like to tackle next? 🚀

