content_list.content:
Here is the complete **HTML/CSS Prototype** for the Apogei 94 Homepage redesign.

### 🚀 How to Use This
1.  **Copy** the code block below.
2.  **Paste** it into a text editor (Notepad, VS Code, TextEdit).
3.  **Save** the file as `apogei-homepage.html`.
4.  **Open** the file in any web browser (Chrome, Firefox, Safari).
5.  **Screenshot** the result to get your PNG visual.

### 🎨 Design System Alignment
*   **Colors:** Directly mapped from your `theme.json` palette (e.g., `#00619b` Brand Blue, `#f9f9f9` Background).
*   **Typography:** Uses `Aptos`/System Sans with sizes from `tokens.json` (H1: 2.5rem, Body: 1rem).
*   **Spacing:** Based on `theme.json` spacing scale (1rem, 1.5rem, etc.).
*   **Accessibility:** Focus states, contrast ratios, and semantic HTML included.

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Apogei 94 - Redesign Prototype</title>
    <style>
        /* -------------------------------------------------------------------------- */
        /* DESIGN SYSTEM TOKENS (Mapped from tokens.json & theme.json)                */
        /* -------------------------------------------------------------------------- */
        :root {
            /* Colors - From theme.json palette */
            --color-bg-default: #f9f9f9;
            --color-bg-surface: #ffffff;
            --color-bg-brand: #00619b;
            --color-bg-brand-subtle: #e6f0f7;
            --color-bg-accent-green: #76b82a;
            --color-bg-accent-magenta: #cc209c;
            --color-text-default: #111111;
            --color-text-secondary: #636363;
            --color-text-inverse: #ffffff;
            --color-text-brand: #00619b;
            --color-border-default: #e5e5e5;
            --color-border-brand: #00619b;
            --color-border-focus: #00619b;

            /* Typography - From tokens.json base.font */
            --font-family: 'Aptos', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            --font-size-h1: 2.5rem; /* 40px */
            --font-size-h2: 2rem;   /* 32px */
            --font-size-h3: 1.5rem; /* 24px */
            --font-size-body: 1rem; /* 16px */
            --font-size-body-lg: 1.125rem; /* 18px */
            --font-weight-regular: 400;
            --font-weight-semibold: 600;
            --font-weight-bold: 700;
            --line-height-body: 1.55;
            --line-height-heading: 1.2;

            /* Spacing - From theme.json spacingSizes */
            --space-xs: 0.5rem;   /* 8px */
            --space-sm: 0.75rem;  /* 12px */
            --space-md: 1rem;     /* 16px */
            --space-lg: 1.5rem;   /* 24px */
            --space-xl: 2rem;     /* 32px */
            --space-2xl: 3rem;    /* 48px */
            --space-3xl: 4rem;    /* 64px */

            /* Radius - From tokens.json semantic.radius */
            --radius-md: 6px;
            --radius-lg: 8px;
            --radius-xl: 16px;
            --radius-full: 9999px;

            /* Shadows - From tokens.json semantic.shadow */
            --shadow-sm: 0 1px 3px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 1px 2px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            --shadow-md: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 2px 4px -2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            --shadow-focus: 0 0 0 3px rgba(0, 97, 155, 0.4);

            /* Layout - From theme.json layout */
            --container-wide: 1280px;
            --container-content: 620px;
        }

        /* -------------------------------------------------------------------------- */
        /* GLOBAL RESET & BASE STYLES                                                 */
        /* -------------------------------------------------------------------------- */
        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        body {
            font-family: var(--font-family);
            background-color: var(--color-bg-default);
            color: var(--color-text-default);
            line-height: var(--line-height-body);
            font-size: var(--font-size-body);
            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
        }

        h1, h2, h3, h4 {
            font-weight: var(--font-weight-semibold);
            line-height: var(--line-height-heading);
            color: var(--color-text-default);
        }

        h1 { font-size: var(--font-size-h1); }
        h2 { font-size: var(--font-size-h2); }
        h3 { font-size: var(--font-size-h3); }

        a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: inherit;
            transition: color 0.2s ease;
        }

        img {
            max-width: 100%;
            display: block;
            border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
        }

        /* Accessibility Focus States */
        :focus-visible {
            outline: 2px solid var(--color-border-focus);
            outline-offset: 2px;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-focus);
        }

        /* Utility Classes */
        .container {
            max-width: var(--container-wide);
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 var(--space-lg);
        }

        .section-padding {
            padding: var(--space-3xl) 0;
        }

        .text-center { text-align: center; }
        .text-brand { color: var(--color-text-brand); }
        .bg-surface { background-color: var(--color-bg-surface); }
        .bg-brand { background-color: var(--color-bg-brand); }
        .text-inverse { color: var(--color-text-inverse); }

        /* -------------------------------------------------------------------------- */
        /* COMPONENTS                                                                 */
        /* -------------------------------------------------------------------------- */

        /* Buttons (From theme.json core/button) */
        .btn {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: var(--space-xs);
            padding: var(--space-xs) var(--space-sm);
            font-size: var(--font-size-body);
            font-weight: var(--font-weight-semibold);
            border-radius: var(--radius-md);
            border: 1px solid transparent;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
            min-height: 44px; /* Touch target */
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background-color: var(--color-bg-brand);
            color: var(--color-text-inverse);
            border-color: var(--color-bg-brand);
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            background-color: #00517f; /* brand hover */
            border-color: #00517f;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
        }

        .btn-outline {
            background-color: transparent;
            color: var(--color-text-brand);
            border-color: var(--color-border-brand);
        }

        .btn-outline:hover {
            background-color: var(--color-bg-brand-subtle);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .btn-ghost {
            background-color: transparent;
            color: var(--color-text-default);
        }

        .btn-ghost:hover {
            background-color: var(--color-bg-subtle);
            color: var(--color-text-brand);
        }

        .btn-lg {
            padding: var(--space-sm) var(--space-md);
            font-size: var(--font-size-body-lg);
        }

        /* Header */
        .header {
            background-color: var(--color-bg-surface);
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border-default);
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
            height: 80px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .header-content {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            width: 100%;
        }

        .logo {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: var(--font-weight-bold);
            color: var(--color-text-brand);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: var(--space-xs);
        }

        .nav-links {
            display: flex;
            gap: var(--space-xl);
            list-style: none;
        }

        .nav-links a {
            font-weight: var(--font-weight-semibold);
            color: var(--color-text-default);
        }

        .nav-links a:hover {
            color: var(--color-text-brand);
        }

        .header-actions {
            display: flex;
            gap: var(--space-sm);
        }

        /* Hero Section */
        .hero {
            position: relative;
            background-color: var(--color-bg-surface);
            padding: var(--space-3xl) 0;
            overflow: hidden;
            min-height: 80vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .hero-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: var(--space-3xl);
            align-items: center;
        }

        .hero-content {
            max-width: 620px;
        }

        .hero-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: var(--color-bg-brand-subtle);
            color: var(--color-text-brand);
            padding: var(--space-xs) var(--space-sm);
            border-radius: var(--radius-full);
            font-size: var(--font-size-body-sm);
            font-weight: var(--font-weight-semibold);
            margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
        }

        .hero-title {
            margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
            font-size: 3.5rem; /* Display size */
            line-height: 1.1;
            letter-spacing: -0.025em;
        }

        .hero-desc {
            font-size: var(--font-size-body-lg);
            color: var(--color-text-secondary);
            margin-bottom: var(--space-2xl);
            max-width: 540px;
        }

        .role-selector {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: var(--space-sm);
            margin-bottom: var(--space-2xl);
        }

        .role-pill {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: var(--space-xs);
            padding: var(--space-xs) var(--space-md);
            border: 1px solid var(--color-border-brand);
            border-radius: var(--radius-full);
            color: var(--color-text-brand);
            font-weight: var(--font-weight-semibold);
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
            background: transparent;
        }

        .role-pill:hover, .role-pill.active {
            background-color: var(--color-bg-brand-subtle);
            border-width: 2px;
        }

        .hero-media {
            position: relative;
            border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
            aspect-ratio: 4/3;
            background-color: #ddd;
        }

        .hero-media img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
            border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
        }

        .play-button {
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            cursor: pointer;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
            transition: transform 0.2s;
        }

        .play-button:hover {
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(1.1);
        }

        /* Impact Strip */
        .impact-strip {
            background-color: var(--color-bg-surface);
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border-default);
            padding: var(--space-lg) 0;
            position: sticky;
            top: 80px;
            z-index: 900;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
        }

        .impact-grid {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: var(--space-lg);
        }

        .stat-item {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .stat-number {
            display: block;
            font-size: var(--font-size-h2);
            font-weight: var(--font-weight-bold);
            color: var(--color-text-brand);
            line-height: 1;
        }

        .stat-label {
            font-size: var(--font-size-body-sm);
            color: var(--color-text-secondary);
            margin-top: var(--space-xs);
        }

        /* Story Grid */
        .story-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: var(--space-lg);
            margin-top: var(--space-2xl);
        }

        .story-card {
            background: var(--color-bg-surface);
            border: 1px solid var(--color-border-default);
            border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
            overflow: hidden;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        .story-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-4px);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
            border-color: var(--color-border-brand);
        }

        .story-media {
            height: 200px;
            background-color: #eee;
            position: relative;
        }

        .story-media img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
            border-radius: 0;
        }

        .story-content {
            padding: var(--space-lg);
            flex: 1;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        .story-tag {
            font-size: var(--font-size-caption);
            color: var(--color-text-brand);
            font-weight: var(--font-weight-semibold);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.05em;
