## 🎯 Key Features Implemented

### ✅ Filtering System (Real JavaScript)
| Feature | Implementation |
|---------|---------------|
| **Pole Filters** | 6 poles from your structure, with chips & select dropdown |
| **Type Toggle** | Tabs: Tous / Établissements / Dispositifs |
| **Search** | Debounced input with name/location/description/tags matching |
| **Location & Age** | Additional filter dimensions with select dropdowns |
| **Active Chips** | Removable filter chips with visual feedback |
| **Clear All** | One-click reset button (appears when filters active) |

### ✅ UX/UI Aligned with Your Tokens
| Token Category | Usage in Code |
|---------------|---------------|
| `semantic.color` | All colors via CSS variables (bg-brand, text-secondary, etc.) |
| `semantic.font` | Typography scale (caption-sm to display-lg) |
| `semantic.space` | Consistent spacing (2xs to 6xl) |
| `semantic.radius` | Border radius (md=6px, lg=8px, xl=16px) |
| `semantic.shadow` | Hover states, focus rings, cards |
| `component.button` | Primary/outline/ghost variants with states |
| `component.badge` | Pole & type badges with semantic colors |

### ✅ Accessibility (WCAG 2.1 AA)
- ✅ Focus states with `:focus-visible` + shadow-focus token
- ✅ ARIA labels for all interactive elements
- ✅ Semantic HTML (`<article>`, `<nav>`, `<main>`)
- ✅ Screen reader announcements for results count
- ✅ Keyboard navigation for cards (Enter/Space to open)
- ✅ Reduced motion support via `@media (prefers-reduced-motion)`
- ✅ Skip link for keyboard users

### ✅ Responsive Design
- Desktop: 3-column grid → Tablet: 2-column → Mobile: 1-column
- Filter bar collapses to vertical stack on mobile
- Touch-friendly targets (min 44px per tokens.json)
- Horizontal scroll for filter chips on small screens

### ✅ Performance Optimized
- Debounced search input (300ms)
- CSS variables for zero runtime calculations
- Lazy-loading images with `loading="lazy"`
- Minimal JavaScript (no external libraries)

